      • instantiateModel

        public Model instantiateModel(String modelId,
                     ModelPlugin pluginHint,
                     boolean ignoreTransientPlugins,
                     boolean forceUseOfPluginHint)
                       throws ModelNotFoundException,
                              ModelInstantiationException
        Instantiate a new Script object. Throws an exception if can't.
        Parameters:
        modelId - See Model.newInstance(ModelPluginEnvironment, String).
        pluginHint - If modelId doesn't specify a plugin, use this plugin hint before looking in other plugins.
        ignoreTransientPlugins - Will ignore plugins marked as transient. Thus new versions of those plugins will be discovered.
        forceUseOfPluginHint - Forces the supplied pluginHint to be used, regardless.
        Returns:
        An instance of Script.
        Throws:
        ModelNotFoundException
        ModelInstantiationException
